'''Treasure Island''' yin owe dé he yin kinkan gbọn [[Robert Louis Stevenson]] dali. E yin zinzinjẹgbonu to owhe 1883 tọn mẹ.
Owe ehe gando jaguda lẹ he yanwẹn adọkunnu de to lopo pevi dé ji.
Mẹhe yin diyin kavi yin tlọntlọngbọn to emẹ wẹ Jim Hawkins, Long John Silver, po Ben Gunn po.
Owe lọ ko tin to aihundida lẹ mẹ, owe aihun nukikodonamẹ tọn, po devo lẹ po.

